    "description": "ValueCommerce Co., Ltd. provides marketing solutions in Japan. It operates through three segments: Marketing Solutions Business, EC Solutions Business, and Travel Tech Business. The company provides performance-based advertising. It offers click-based advertising and CRM tools for online mall stores; and DYNA IBE, a hotel reservation system provided for accommodation facilities such as hotels and inns. In addition, the company provides DYNA PMS, a hotel management system; VLINK, a social commerce platform; monicam and Cast book, an influencer marketing solution; B-Space, an EC site management and support solution; and BUZMA, a subscription-based influencer matching service. The company was formerly known as Transpacific Inc. and changed its name to ValueCommerce Co., Ltd. in November 1999. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Chiyoda, Japan. ValueCommerce Co., Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Z Holdings Corporation."
